===Etymology===
Inherited from {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*da(k)}}. Cognate with {{cog|bo|འདས||to pass over}}.

{{cog|tai-pro|*daːᴮ||river}} (whence {{cog|th|ท่า||port; pier; quay}} and {{cog|za|dah||river}}) is a loan from late {{cog|och|-}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}).

The Austroasiatic synonym of {{lang|zh|渡}} is {{och-l|濟|to cross a river}}.

